message: Hi Bob, I'm offering you my product for $10,000.  I think it's a great deal for both of us, considering its value to you. Let me know what you think!

Hello Alice, thank you for your offer. I appreciate the value of the product, but I am looking to keep my expenses lower. Would it be possible for us to negotiate the price down to $9,000? I believe this would still be a fair deal for both of us.
